caption.text:
Shopee: Melestarikan Warisan Budaya _ Cha Yuan Ming Cha, Taiwan

Xu Qiongwen meneruskan warisan keluarganya dengan mengambil alih usaha dan membangun Cha Yuan Ming Cha, sebuah brand online yang memperkenalkan kekayaan budaya teh Taiwan kepada generasi baru pecinta teh.

Saksikan “Shopee: Melestarikan Warisan Budaya” dan rayakan jutaan UMKM di seluruh Asia Tenggara, Taiwan dan Brasil yang terus tumbuh bersama Shopee, sambil menjaga keunikan budaya mereka.

--
Xu Qiongwen champions her family’s legacy by taking over the business and building Cha Yuan Ming Cha, an online brand that introduces Taiwan’s tea heritage to a new generation of tea drinkers.

Watch Shopee: Keeping Cultures Alive and celebrate the MSME sellers across Southeast Asia, Taiwan, and Brazil who have built their businesses while preserving their unique cultures.

#Shopee #Shopee10thBirthday #KeepingCulturesAlive
